DARNELL JOHNSON v. COMMISSIONER OF CORRECTION (14856)

Lavery, Heiman and Hennessy, Js.

Argued February 16 decision released March 12, 1996 Mei-wa Cheng, with whom, on the brief, was Carrie A. Howard, for the appellant (petitioner). L. D. McCallum, assistant attorney general, with whom, on the brief, was Richard Blumenthal, attorney general, for the appellee (respondent). PER CURIAM.

The judgment is affirmed.
